# Project Intelligence Rules
1. All code follows Python best practices and PEP 8
2. Three-stage pipeline is core architecture pattern
3. Performance is critical - target <5s for 20 pages
4. Modular design with clear component boundaries
5. Environment variables in .env for configuration
6. Comprehensive error handling and logging
7. Test coverage essential for all components
8. Documentation must be clear and up-to-date
9. Memory efficiency is a key consideration
10. CLI interface should be simple and intuitive
